def solve(r, g, b):
    r = r/255
    g = g/255
    b = b/255
    
    c_max = max(r, g, b)
    c_min = min(r, g, b)
    delta = c_max - c_min
    
    #Hue calculation
    if delta == 0:
        h = 0
    elif c_max == r:
        h = ((g-b)/delta) % 6
    elif c_max == g:
        h = ((b-r)/delta) + 2
    else:
        h = ((r-g)/delta) + 4
    h = round(h*60)
    
    #Saturation calculation
    if c_max == 0:
        s = 0
    else:
        s = delta/c_max
    s = round(s*100)
    
    #Value calculation
    v = c_max
    v = round(v*100)
    
    return (h, s, v)
